==========================
INSTALLATION
==========================

These instructions are for the webapp in /webserver/ only:

The app requires Ruby 1.8.7 and Rails 2.3.15, and uses Bundler for gem management. By default it is set up to use sqlite3.

Prerequisites:

* If needed: `apt-get install sqlite3`
* RMagick dependencies are required: `apt-get install libmagickwand-devlibmagick++-dev`
  * or on centOs: `yum install ImageMagick-devel`
  * On mac, you can use Homebrew: `brew install imagemagick`
* Recommended -- use RVM: http://rvm.io
* `rvm install 1.8.7`

Installation steps:

* `bundle install`
* `rake db:migrate`
* `passenger start`

